   Why WordPress Hosting?

Why is our WordPress Hosting for India is different?

   WordPress is truly massive. 28% of all known websites use WordPress as
   their preferred content management system. Why? It's simple and easy to
   learn and once mastered provides you with a world of possibilities.
   Thousands of plugins, templates and other tools help WordPress users
   create sophisticated online stores, blogs, portfolios and other kinds
   of websites. Some of the biggest companies in the world use WordPress.
   Be part of the community and start your website now!

Diverse and Powerful

   Due to WordPress being an open-source platform, it was put to use for
   many different projects. Talented developers have figured out ways to
   use this CMS with unbelievable results. E-commerce, blog, community or
   portfolio. WordPress does it all but with Hostinger can do even more!

Cheap and Beginner-Friendly

   WordPress hosting with Hostinger paves a clear road towards success. We
