WordPress hosting: Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

   Answers to frequently asked questions about WordPress and WordPress
   hosting.

What is WordPress?

   It is the most popular CMS in the world. WordPress is a content
   management system that you can install on your server and build a
   website around. The platform is based on PHP and is open-source. Over a
   quarter of all sites use this CMS. Both experts and novices consider
   WordPress as the most straightforward and flexible content management
   system on the market. The best part about WordPress is that it has
   incredible potential and can fit almost any project while being easily
   learnable at the same time.

What kind of website can I create on WordPress?

   The short answer: almost anything! WordPress is incredibly diverse. You
   can build a complex e-commerce site, blog, affiliate website and much
   more! This trait made WordPress the most popular CMS on Earth. If
   you're looking for a platform that will help you build a robust web
   presence, WordPress should be among your top choices! WordPress is a
   prime example of how to give power to the people the right way. If you
   run into roadblocks while building your website, remember that
   WordPress has one of the largest online communities, that create
   hundreds of tutorials, articles, walkthroughs and other content.

How WordPress hosting is different from regular web hosting?

   WordPress has nearly unparalleled efficiency, performance and
   resources. We have developed custom tools, that optimise your WordPress
   hosting experience, and implemented must-have features like WP-CLI, GIT
   and SSH. If you think WordPress hosting is for you, take the chance and
   get started in just a few clicks! Sign up, use our auto-installer tool
   and begin your project! Once you're up and running, take advantage of
   pre-installed caching plugins and many other features that will take
   the speed and performance of your website to the next level.

How to get started after purchasing Hostinger’s WordPress hosting?

   Once you've signed up, it'll take just a few clicks! All you have to do
   is navigate to our control panel, choose the WordPress option on our
   auto-installer and log into your WordPress panel once the installation
   is complete! Logging in is as simple as going to a dedicated URL like
   www.exampledomain.in/wp-admin. We made this process as quick and
   straightforward as possible, all for your convenience.

Can I transfer my WordPress website that is hosted with a different provider
to Hostinger?

   Of course! And we made the process more natural than most other hosting
   providers. Your WordPress website can be moved over in a single click
   in one seamless process. No need to worry about downtimes and growing
   pains. If by chance some issue would come up, you won't be alone in
   solving it! Our fanatically dedicated customer support team will help
   you through the process, 24/7/365.

Is your WordPress version different from WordPress.org version?

   You will get the very same version as WordPress.org. At Hostinger we
   aim to give our users power, and power comes from staying on the
   cutting-edge. As soon as you sign up, you'll be able to work with the
   latest version of WordPress! No need to worry about updates: enable the
   automatic update features, and our auto-installer will make sure that
   you are always up to date, every time a new release is out. Build
   without limits, install all the themes or plugins you need and
   customise your site until it's perfect. You can access and work on core
   WordPress files too!

Is Hostinger secure enough to host WordPress?

   You can't call yourself a great web hosting provider if you don't take
   security seriously! That's why we invest in our security solutions. Our
   first line of defence is BitNinja - a cutting-edge server security
   provider. BitNinja equips our servers with sophisticated malware
   detection and removal tools, intrusion detection and protection against
   DDoS attacks. The infrastructure provided by this service makes sure
   that the use of collective intelligence makes all servers entirely
   secure. We also take advantage of web honeypots and other features that
   guarantee defence against potentially fatal attacks. You can sleep
   easy, knowing that you're safe with Hostinger.

WordPress Hosting is a minute away!

   You can start your WordPress website within a minute! Register, pick a
   plan that fits your needs and use our 1-click WordPress installer. Get
   access to the world’s most popular CMS and expand your web presence.
   Some of the most prominent businesses in the world use WordPress, and
   you can be among them. With Hostinger you can get the most out of
   WordPress Hosting.
   Setup WordPress NOW

